<item>
            <title>[HBASE-18] [hbase] A sequence of create/delete/create/etc. generates &apos;info:regioninfo is empty; has keys:&apos; and eventually fails</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-18</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Marking as minor issue since its a concurrency issue in admin function.  Though that said, this is a guaranteed way to generate rows in META that are without their regioninfo (Looks like we might add startcode and servername after a row has had its regioninfo removed).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Issue was found by Dave Simpson running a create/delete/create sequence.  Attaching log.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
